Process called "f256_shift_right256_sticky_one" takes l0_in as Integer, l1_in as Integer, l2_in as Integer, l3_in as Integer, sticky_in as Integer, out0 as Integer, out1 as Integer, out2 as Integer, out3 as Integer, out_sticky as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Shift a 256-bit value right by 1 bit, OR shifted-out bit into sticky.
